ced modeling the dynamics and the\nmass distribution of elliptical galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Jul 2017 11:41:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Nov 2017 14:01:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-20"}
